    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Flying Saucer,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "a weapon tested in 1944, which is probably now being produced in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "series, and at this time causes a great stir, is a V-weapon which",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "has a round body similar to a disk having a diameter of about",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "42-50 m. On the outer ring it has about 45-50 automatic circular",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "nozzles which after the ignition of the disk circulate around a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "plexiglass sphere in the center in which the measuring and controlling",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "devices for long-distance steering are located. In the sphere is still",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "sufficient space for atom bombs. These weapons are in Russian hands",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "and can have an effective range of 30-35,000 km. The constructor of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "V-weapons RIEDEL in Germany stated that it concerns a typical V-weapon",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
